{DIALOGUE}: You don't want to be on this ship for the rest of your life.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMY
{DIALOGUE}: I do.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 31.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES
{DIALOGUE}: No, you don't, Jimmy.
