{DIALOGUE}: Why would they get spooked?
{DIALOGUE}: What's it called?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DENHAM looks SHIFTY.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DENHAM
{DIALOGUE}: All right ... It has a local name, but I'm warning you, Jack, it doesn't sound good.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JIMMY, his attention caught as he eavesdrops on the conversation.
