{CHARACTER_NAME}: DENHAM (cont'd)
{META_DATA}: (quietly)
{DIALOGUE}: They call it ...
{META_DATA}: (muffled)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JIMMY POV: DENHAM leaning in and murmuring to JACK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 36.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: What's wrong with this place?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DENHAM
{DIALOGUE}: There's nothing officially wrong with it.
{DIALOGUE}: Because technically it hasn't been discovered yet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK gives up, feeling too seasick to argue ...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{META_DATA}: (resuming typing)
{DIALOGUE}: Okay ... alright ... so we arrive at ( this place ... typing) S ... k ... u ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: DENHAM looks up in time to see JIMMY listening ... Their eyes meet ... DENHAM tries to hush JACK - too late.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: l ... l ... Island.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE/OCEAN - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: The SHIP moves through GREY SEAS ... Dolphins swim alongside.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE DECK - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IDE ON: DENHAM is FILMING ANN and BRUCE.
