{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE/OCEAN - DUSK
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IDE ON: THE VENTURE steams on as the SUN falls slowly behind the horizon ...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. MESS ROOM - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM & PRESTON are seated at a table, talking quietly.
