{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE- FOGGY NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: RUNCH!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The BOW of the SHIP crumples in to the WALL!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 51.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE DECKS - FOGGY NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGEL ON: ANN rushes out of a door, on to the DECK, alarmed at the PANIC on the SHIP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM looks in utter AWE at the WALL.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. VENTURE WHEELHOUSE - FOGGY NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ENGLEHORN yells at HAYES.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ENGLEHORN
{DIALOGUE}: Give me some power!
{DIALOGUE}: Half astern, both!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES
{DIALOGUE}: Half astern, both, Captain!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE DECKS - FOGGY NIGHT
