{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. NATIVE VILLAGE/WALL - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN being DRAGGED through a FRENZY OF FEARFUL Skull Island NATIVES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GLIMPSES of WAILING ... COWERING ... CHANTING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FLAMES BLAZE along the TOP OF THE WALL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: A withered old WOMAN, EYES RED in some DRUG induced TRANCE, speaks in TONGUES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN is forced to her knees.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The OLD WOMAN splashes some foul LIQUID into her face ... younger WOMEN tie BRACELETS on her wrists.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE DECKS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: COVERS are pulled off lifeboats as the SHIP'S CREW gather EQUIPMENT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: HAYES yelling commands:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES
{DIALOGUE}: All hands going ashore ...
{META_DATA}: CRASH CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. ENGLEHORN'S CABIN - NIGHT
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES V/O
{DIALOGUE}: ... report to stations!
{DIALOGUE}: Jump to it!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ENGLEHORN LIFTS UP THE WINDOW SEAT ... revealing a ROW of TOMMY GUNS hidden there.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLES ON: GUNS are handed out.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE DECKS - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: EQUIPMENT and RIFLES are THROWN IN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ENTIRE SHIP'S CREW is MOBILIZING.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: What the hell are you doing?
{DIALOGUE}: You want that boat to sink?
{DIALOGUE}: Stow those rifles midships - come on, hurry it up!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 64.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM surreptitiously supervises HERB and PRESTON as they load CAMERA EQUIPMENT on board one of the BOATS ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK loading a BOX of AMMUNITION on to the other BOAT ... he looks tensely at the FIRES burning on the ISLAND.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: The TWO BOATS are swung out and LOWERED.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Lower away!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VENTURE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: he TWO BOATS ROW AWAY from the SHIP, packed with SHIP'S CREW ... in one BOAT are DENHAM, PRESTON and HERB - clutching CAMERA EQUIPMENT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK in the OTHER BOAT, looking GRIM and DETERMINED.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SKULL ISLAND COAST - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: the TINY BOATS are tossed in the RAGING SEAS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SAILORS try to STEER them towards the SHORE, as they bounce off ROCKS and STATUES.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. TOP OF WALL - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOSE ON: FLAMING TORCHES ignite POOLS of OIL along the length of the TOP of the WALL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLES ON: ANN'S WRIST'S are TIED outstretched to BAMBOO POSTS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is on the SUMMIT of the WALL, lit by the flickering FLAMES ... looking out onto DARK TREE TOPS.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: F
{DIALOGUE}: LAMES DANCE ... DRUMS BEAT in a RITUALISTIC FRENZY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SKULL ISLANDERS knock away WOODEN PLUGS, releasing the FLAMING OIL to pour down rough CHANNELS hewn into the STONE of the WALL ... it runs and falls down CHUTES into POOLS carved into the GROTTO WALLS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: The CLIFF WALLS light up as FLAMES within LARGE CARVED CHAMBERS create huge backlit PAGAN FACES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FIRELIGHT dances across the nightmarish JUNGLE ... DISTANT TREES start to TREMBLE, their canopies swaying as if PUSHED by an UNSEEN FORCE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN ... looking on with HORROR at the MOVEMENT in the JUNGLE below her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She struggles against the ROPES, to no avail.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: The OLD WOMAN, eyes rolled up in her head.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOSE ON: A NECKLACE is placed over ANN'S head.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 65.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: A SHAMAN starts BEATING out a RHYTHM on a LOG DRUM ... SKULL ISLANDERS fall to their KNEES ... a MOANING WAIL rises ... the DRUMMING builds to a FRENZIED CLIMAX.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: On the OTHER SIDE, the WALL falls away vertically into a ROCKY GROTTO, leading into the DENSE TANGLED JUNGLE of SKULL ISLAND.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY ANN feels herself DRAGGED FORWARD ... the POSTS she is tied to are MOVING, pulling her TOWARDS the EDGE of the WALL!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN digs her heels and tries to PULL AGAINST it, but is unable to stop herself being HAULED OFF THE WALL ... .
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: into thin air!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: SKULL ISLANDERS lowering the BAMBOO ALTAR STRUCTURE DOWN, slowly releasing the flaxen ROPE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN is dangling from the POSTS by her WRISTS, as the HINGED FRAMEWORK swings her out over the CHASM, LOWERING her towards a ROCK PROMONTORY on the EDGE of the FOREST.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN is LOWERED onto the ROCK PROMONTORY, which resembles an ALTAR ... ANN struggles to free herself, but she is tied fast to the posts, a TINY FIGURE illuminated by enormous GLOWING CARVINGS ... the WALL towering up behind her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLES ON: ANN squirms ... as the FOREST BELOW HER BROILS and SEETHES!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TREES are violently SWAYING ... above the crescendo of the NATIVE FRENZY, ANGRY BESTIAL ROARS can be heard.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SKULL ISLANDERS line the TOP of the WALL, their WAILING and CHANTING interrupted by a LOUD SPLINTERING SOUND.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SKULL ISLAND SHORE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SHIP'S BOATS pull up at the foot of the great STAIRCASE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK leaps out of the BOAT and races up the stairs.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. WALL GROTTO - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN lifts her head ... something VERY BIG is moving towards HER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN catches a BRIEF GLIMPSE of a HUGE DARK SHAPE propelling itself THROUGH the JUNGLE ... the OILY SMOKE from the FIRES hangs in the air, OBSCURING HER VISION ... she can now only hear the CREATURE'S MOVEMENTS and BREATH as it draws ever closer.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN cowers back, pulling at her bonds.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A MASSIVE SHAPE moves through the air ... The ground SHAKES with a sudden force of IMPACT!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN stands trembling, as the swirling smokey cloud slowly DISSIPATES ... a GIANT LEATHERY FOOT is visible.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN balanced on a knife-edge of TERROR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 66.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A SUDDEN PUFF OF WIND INSTANTLY CLEARS THE VEILING SMOKE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN slowly LOOKS UP, her face filled with DREAD.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SKULL ISLANDERS reply in UNISON ... a piercing WAIL, from the TOP of the WALL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN'S strength suddenly DRAINS from her legs, and SLUMPS between the POSTS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Before her is ... KONG!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A 25 FOOT TALL MALE GORILLA!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG stares at ANN for a beat, leaning forward on his KNUCKLES ... then prods her with his finger.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY ... GUNSHOTS!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. NATIVE VILLAGE/WALL - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FRENZIED MOVEMENT: SAILORS, lead by ENGLEHORN, race into the VILLAGE firing WARNING SHOTS in the air ... SKULL ISLANDERS SCATTER in TERROR ...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. WALL GROTTO - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IDE ON: KONG in front of ANN ... HE RISES to his full height and BEATS HIS CHEST!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG'S HUGE HAND snatches ANN and roughly PULLS her free of her bonds.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DEAFENING ROAR!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN SCREAMS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLUTCHING her tightly, KONG carries ANN away from the ALTAR.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. NATIVE VILLAGE/WALL - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FRENZIED MOVEMENT: SAILORS, lead by ENGLEHORN, race into the VILLAGE firing WARNING SHOTS in the air ... SKULL ISLANDERS SCATTER in TERROR ...
