{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SKULL ISLAND JUNGLE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: The VOLCANIC ROCKS form a JAGGED, TORTURED LANDSCAPE of DEEP CREVASSES and TOWERING CLIFFS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The vegetation is THICK, the JUNGLE DARK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANCIENT GNARLED TREES twist out of the ground, thick LICHEN and long MOSSES hang from branches and TANGLED VINES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: STEAM RISES from festering SWAMPS ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 69.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HAYES is LEADING DENHAM, JACK, PRESTON, LUMPY, CHOY, BRUCE and EIGHT SAILORS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HERB is limping along with the heavy CAMERA on his shoulder.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The atmosphere is TENSE ... unseen creatures scurry in the darkness, fleeing from the approaching humans.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HAYES puts his hands up ... the GROUP stops ... a STRANGE, LOW MOAN echoes from the SURROUNDING JUNGLE ... The MEN stare into the darkness ... watchful, on edge ...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. KILLING GROUND - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN in KONG'S HAND, being tossed around like a rag doll as KONG RUNS through the FOREST.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: KONG propels himself through the JUNGLE with EASE, barely disturbing the forest, moving with GRACE along a well used route.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOSE ON: ANN held fast in his GRIP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is FLUNG wildly around as KONG BOUNDS across CHASMS, LEAPING over rivers.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN'S FEVERED POV: The JUNGLE SPINNING and BLURRING by.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She tries to brace herself against KONG'S FINGERS, but the rigors of the journey knock her sideways like a RAG DOLL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: SHAFTS of MOONLIGHT play on the faces of grotesque STATUES set into a MOSSY CLIFF.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN clutched tightly in KONG'S HAND.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is rigid with FEAR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG squats down ... he LOOKS CLOSELY at ANN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: KONG ... we see him clearly for the first time.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A very old, brutish BULL GORILLA.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Years of survival have left SCARS on his face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: One EYE LID is mangled and his JAW is CROOKED ... leaving a huge yellowed INCISOR TOOTH jutting up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG stares at ANN ... she dare not move; only her RAPID BREATHING belies her INNER TERROR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN is suddenly swung UPSIDE DOWN and SHAKEN ... the ceremonial NECKLACE falls from ANN'S NECK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN'S HORRIFIED FACE ... she sees HUMAN REMAINS amongst the NECKLACES!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bones ... skulls!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A WHIMPERING SOUND escapes from the back of her throat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SWIRLING UPSIDE DOWN POV: The NECKLACE lands on the ground - amid DOZENS of OTHER NECKLACES littering the clearing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN is lifted UPWARDS ... KONG'S LIPS curl in a low, slow SNARL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN looks at KONG, aghast, and in this moment her heightened sense of FEAR gives way to something more fundamental: SELF PRESERVATION!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 70.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG'S FINGERS start to OPEN - ANN seizes her chance!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She suddenly PROPELS herself off his HAND!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN DROPS 12 feet and lands heavily at KONG'S FEET.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She rolls amongst grinning HUMAN SKULLS and LEG BONES ... staggers to her feet and RUNS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG rises up with a ROAR, but ANN is already disappearing into the JUNGLE!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. DENSE JUNGLE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLES ON: ANN desperately powering through the DENSE UNDERGROWTH.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She throws herself over huge FALLEN LOGS, through TANGLED VINES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She GLANCES BACK ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TREES are FALLING, KONG is smashing through the undergrowth after her!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: With surprising AGILITY and GRACE, KONG sweeps down from above and SCOOPS ANN off the ROCK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She barely has time to CRY OUT before being CARRIED AWAY, as KONG disappears into the DEPTHS of the ISLAND.
