{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is half way across the clearing when she TRIPS and FALLS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: KONG bounds over to ANN, SLAPPING his HANDS on the GROUND in a frenzy of excitement - he utters a GUTTERAL SQUEAL.
