{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ... ANN SPRINGS UP, looks at KONG for a desperate moment, wonders if she should run, decides she'll never make it ... and takes another PRATFALL!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG cocks his HEAD!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He GRIMACES, baring his teeth and CIRCLES her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN repeats the COMIC FALL!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG SLAPS his HANDS on the GROUND, SHAKES his HEAD and GROWLS.
