{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. LOG CHASM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IDE ANGLE: DENHAM, JACK, HAYES, LUMPY, JIMMY, PRESTON and the remaining CREW have arrived at a DARK, VINE ENTANGLED CHASM ... spanning the narrow, but deadly RAVINE is a SINGLE FALLEN TREE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WEAK SUNLIGHT filters through the DARK CANOPY above casting a SICKLY GREEN HUE over the place.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IDE ON: HAYES, followed by JIMMY, leads the GROUP across the SLIMY, MOSS covered LOG ... the going is treacherous.
