{DIALOGUE}: Get Jimmy out of here.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: HAYES... SHOOTS into the DARKNESS of the TUNNEL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG rampages out of the TUNNEL MOUTH!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He SNATCHES HAYES with one SWEEP of his HAND.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: HAYES in KONG's HAND ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IMMY yells!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG's GAZE turns toward the MEN on the LOG!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMY
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{DIALOGUE}: Let him go!
{META_DATA}: (to HAYES)
{DIALOGUE}: Kill him!
{DIALOGUE}: Kill him!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES
{META_DATA}: (to KONG)
{DIALOGUE}: Look at me!
{DIALOGUE}: Look at me!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMY
{META_DATA}: (desperate)
{DIALOGUE}: Bring him down!
{DIALOGUE}: Mr Hayes!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SLOWLY HAYES begins to lift his PISTOL up ... KONG's GAZE locks back on HAYES ...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES
{DIALOGUE}: deadly calm) You've gotta run, Jimmy.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: IMMY
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{DIALOGUE}: I ain't gonna run.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES
{DIALOGUE}: Do as I say.
{META_DATA}: (to JIMMY)
{CHARACTER_NAME}: G
{DIALOGUE}: o with Jack ... All of you.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG stares at HAYES a BEAT ... HAYES suddenly raises his PISTOL at KONG to shoot!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 85.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAYES (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: KONG HURLS HAYES at the SAILORS ... he flies over their heads like RAG-DOLL and smashes against the FAR WALL of the RAVINE with a sickening CRUNCH.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMY
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JIMMY runs at KONG, blinded by tears of GRIEF and RAGE ... JACK KNOCKS him down and SHOOTS at KONG.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{META_DATA}: (desperate)
{DIALOGUE}: Shoot him!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WILD SHOOTING from the SAILORS, as they try to maintain BALANCE on the LOG.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG ROARS ... DESPERATE SAILORS try to back across the RAVINE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG runs towards the LOG ... KONG'S FIST smashes at the LOG, knocking the men off balance.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A SAILOR plummets off into the CHASM below.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. THICK JUNGLE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN hurrying through the JUNGLE ... hearing the sound of gun fire.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN
{DIALOGUE}: Hey!
{DIALOGUE}: Here!
{DIALOGUE}: Over here!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She runs up the bank towards the noise.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. FAR EDGE OF CHASM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IDE ON: KONG has LIFTED the END of the LOG!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK, DENHAM, LUMPY, CHOY, JIMMY, PRESTON and THREE SAILORS hold on for dear life ... as KONG vigorously TWISTS and SHAKES the LOG, bucking the MEN into the air.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM skates on the MOSS and his CAMERA slides away, becoming WEDGED in the fork of a STUMP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LL AROUND panicked SAILORS are SHOOTING WILDLY, but fear and lack of balance throws their AIM OFF.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WO SAILORS FALL ... CHOY scrambles for something to grab.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHOY
{DIALOGUE}: Lumpy!
{DIALOGUE}: Help me!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LUMPY desperately tries to reach CHOY'S hand ... but CHOY slips away into the ABYSS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 86.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG ROARS with FRUSTRATION, and TOSSES the ENTIRE LOG into the CHASM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: QUICK IMAGE: DENHAM, PRESTON, JACK, JIMMY and LUMPY gripping the LOG as it FALLS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: QUICK IMAGE: PRESTON thrown off the LOG halfway down ... he manages to GRAB onto a ROCKY SHELF.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: PRESTON is nearest to the FAR BANK ... he LEAPS, and MANAGES to catch hold of some hanging VINES, hauling himself up to safety.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: The LOG plummets into a web of VINES, which arrest its FALL and sends it FLIPPING end on end, throwing the MEN CLEAR into mid-air... DENHAM, JACK and LUMPY land in SOFT MUD which cushions the impact of the LANDING.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VALLEY EDGE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN suddenly spins around ... the DISTANT SOUND of approaching FOOTSTEPS through the dense JUNGLE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A flicker of hope in ANN'S eyes!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She starts hurrying towards the FOOTSTEPS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN sees a distant PLUME of SMOKE - over FOUR MILES AWAY ... she hesitates.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She SLOWLY turns towards the SOUND of the FOOTSTEPS, which are now VERY CLOSE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly a LARGE 8 foot tall CARNIVOROUS DINOSAUR is in the GLADE before her!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN as she quietly backtracks.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The CARNIVORE pauses, as if SENSING something.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's NOSTRILS twitch.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She ducks behind a WIDE TREE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN PEERING around from behind the TREE ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ... there is another CARNIVORE BEHIND HER!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It snares at her ... and pounces!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN leaps away ... she barely has time to start running before the CARNIVORE GIVES CHASE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN races past the first CARNIVORE ... the creature turns it's head ... and soon BOTH DINOSAURS are pursuing ANN.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. HOLLOW TREE GLADE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN desperately heads towards the TANGLED ROOT SYSTEM of a HUGE TREE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She throws herself forward, as the CARNIVORE'S JAWS snap above her head.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN ROLLS and SCRAMBLES into a HOLLOW under the ROTTEN TREE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: The CARNIVORE CLAW at the TREE, trying to get at ANN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 87.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN is lying beneath the ROOTS ... all she can see are LEGS and SLAVERING SNOUTS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The DINOSAUR RAM'S it's nose into the NARROW GAP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY ... ANN sees the LEGS of one of her pursuers LIFT off the GROUND - it's taloned feet thrashing in mid-air.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: he SECOND CARNIVORE turns and FLEES into the JUNGLE, as ANN is forced to watch the twitching legs SHUDDER and FLAIL.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SOUND of BONE CRUNCHING ... CRACK!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The CARNIVORE'S LEGS SPASM and go limp.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN is completely still, she dare not breathe ... whatever killed the CARNIVORE is now inches from her hiding PLACE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN'S FACE ... as she sees something CRAWLING above her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: A DARK HOLE, beneath the tree ... Long FEELERS probe along the ROOF of the hole as a HUGE CENTIPEDE CRAWLS towards her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN doesn't move as it inches towards her face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly she feels another crawling up over her shoulder.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN FREAKS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She desperately scrambles away from the CENTIPEDES ... rolls out on the OTHER SIDE of the TREE and stands to RUN...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ... TOWERING above her, with the DEAD CARNIVORE hanging limply from it's HUGE JAWS, is a TYRANNOSAURUS REX!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN starts RUNNING!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The TYRANNOSAUR crashes after her with the DEAD CARNIVORE still in it's MOUTH... as SHE races through the JUNGLE, dodging TREES, leaping over FALLEN LOGS, smashing through BUSHES, the TYRANNOSAUR POUNDING ever closer in pursuit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN can feel its hot sour BREATH blowing on the back of her neck!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The HUGE JAWS of the HUGE BEAST open INCHES from ANN'S HEAD!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. VALLEY EDGE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: ANN slips down a MUDDY BANK, rolls over a LOG, and CRASHES NOISILY through a THICKET of PALMS ...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. FALLEN TREE GLADE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN'S LUNGS are bursting, but the TYRANNOSAUR is GAINING on her ... she manages to scramble onto a FALLEN TREE that juts out over a small CLIFF.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN clings onto the MOSSY LOG, and crawls towards the END ... the TYRANNOSAUR cannot possibly follow her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She falls amongst the roots, lying as flat as possible, praying the TYRANNOSAUR doesn't see her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It seems to work and IT walks off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN HESITANTLY SITS up, thinking that she is at last free, only to turn and discover another is behind her!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: With an almost delicate movement, the TYRANNOSAUR nudges the LOG with it's head ... causing it to lurch dramatically!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The TYRANNOSAUR pushes HARDER, sending ANN over the SIDE ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 88.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: she just manages to grab hold of a BRANCH as she FALLS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN hangs on desperately ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHE SCREAMS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN is HELPLESS ... The TYRANNOSAUR positions it's HEAD for the FINAL LUNGE - gaping JAWS OPEN impossibly WIDE ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: AT THAT MOMENT: KONG CHARGES!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG meets the TYRANNOSAUR HEAD-ON at FULL SPEED!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He swings, with his FOOT smashing the TYRANNOSAUR against the FALLEN LOG ... ANN loses her GRASP and FALLS ... as the DINOSAUR SPRAWLS onto the ground beside her ... in a flash, KONG CATCHES HER mid-fall ... ROLLING AWAY as the TYRANNOSAUR LEAPS UP and tries to take another swipe.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SKULL ISLAND JUNGLES - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: AST FEVERED ACTION: A pair of CARNIVOROUS DINOSAURS leap towards HER!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They cling onto KONG'S ARM, clawing furiously, snapping at ANN!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOSE ON: Saliva flies from wild, snapping jaws.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: KONG rolls over, THUMPING his arm against a TREE, crushing a DINOSAUR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN is WINDED ... she clings to KONG'S FINGERS as he strangles the second BEAST with one hand, snapping it's NECK with a BONE CRUNCHING sound.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: UDDENLY!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A SECOND TYRANNOSAUR ATTACKS!!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He comes charging into shot, grabbing KONG'S ARM in his JAWS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG ROARS, sending both TYRANNOSAURS SPRAWLING TO THE GROUND.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The FIRST TYRANNOSAUR scrambles back to it's feet!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG holds ANN protectively as he braces himself for the FIGHT OF HIS LIFE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The TWO TYRANNOSAURS CIRCLE him ... when SUDDENLY!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A THIRD TYRANNOSAUR comes from behind.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: T
{DIALOGUE}: hey ATTACK KONG and ANN ... a BREATHTAKING FIGHT to the DEATH.
{DIALOGUE}: KONG fights like a madman on three separate fronts ... Not only does he have to do battle with the TYRANNOSAURS, he is also PROTECTING ANN - constantly transferring her from ONE HAND to THE OTHER as the TYRANNOSAURS SNAP AT HER HEELS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG punches and smashes with his fists, but he also uses wrestling-style headlocks and flips ... for a brief moment, ANN rolls free on the ground and has to dodge 25-foot DINOSAURS and the GORILLA, as the frenzied fight THUNDERS all around her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The FIRST TYRANNOSAUR is taken out when KONG LIFTS up a HUGE BOULDER and SMASHES it against the TYRANNOSAUR'S HEAD.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG and the TWO TYRANNOSAURS slide down on to a ROCKY OUTCROP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG outs the SECOND TYRANNOSAUR in a HEADLOCK, FLIPPING it over his shoulder, and throwing it down into the CHASM.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLINGING ONTO THE LEDGE KONG PULLS THE FIRST TYRANNOSAUR OFF THE LEDGE ... BUT AS IT FALLS it SNAPS AT KONG'S FOOT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: E
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 89.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG ROARS IN PAIN AND TOGETHER THEY FALL DOWN INTO THE CHASM ... DOWN INTO THE VINES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG CONTINUES TO FIGHT THE TYRANNOSAUR, AS ANN IS LEFT SWINGING, CAUGHT UP IN THE VINES ... TOWARDS THE SECOND TYRANNOSAUR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE SNAPS AT HER AS SHE COMES WITHIN INCHES OF HIS JAW.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: KONG SEES AND CLIMBS UP TOWARDS IT, PULLING IT DOWN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THEY ALL TUMBLE DEEPER INTO THE CHASM, AND SUDDENLY ANN FINDS HERSELF DANGLING FROM THE JAWS OF THE TYRANNOSAUR ABOVE THE JAWS OF ANOTHER!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG SWINGS AND KICKS THE TYRANNOSAUR IN THE HEAD ... ANN LOSES HER GRIP AND PLUMMETS DOWN ... VINES BREAKING AS SHE FALLS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: AND more SMASHING AGAINST THE CHASM WALLS ... SHE FALLS AND LANDS ON THE HEAD OF ANOTHER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FALLS AGAIN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHE LANDS IN THE SWAMP.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: RUNS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IT CHASES.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. CLEARING - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: ANN faces the TYRANNOSAUR!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY KONG THUDS DOWN BEHIND HER ... GLARING AT THE DINOSAUR ... ANN FINDS HERSELF CAUGHT BETWEEN THE TWO BEASTS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN WEIGHS UP HER OPTIONS BETWEEN BOTH ... and for a moment ANN & KONG LOCK EYES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHE THEN BACKS BENEATH THE LOOMING FIGURE OF KONG.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: T
{DIALOGUE}: HE TYRANNOSAUR SNARLS at KONG and he ROARS BACK ... KONG THROWS ANN GENTLY to the side as HE and the TYRANNOSAUR LUNGE at each other.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG GRABS HIS JAWS in BOTH HANDS forcing it OPEN and BITING the TYRANNOSAUR'S TONGUE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE ROLLS the TYRANNOSAUR over and over, using all his strength to force the TYRANNOSAUR'S JAWS OPEN before RIPPING them clean APART at the HINGE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The TYRANNOSAUR sprawls back, DEAD.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG is PANTING HEAVILY ... he has been BITTEN, RAKED and CUT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He puts his foot on the LAST TYRANNOSAUR and BEATS HIS CHEST, TRIUMPHANTLY with a DEAFENING ROAR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: KONG KICKS THE DINOSAUR OUT THE WAY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG ROARS ANGRILY - his blood is up, he is ready to take on the world.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE STANDS NEXT TO ANN, BUT HE WON'T LOOK AT HER DIRECTLY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SHE TRIES TO HIS ATTENTION BUT HE LOOKS AWAY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE LUMBERS AWAY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG has DEADLY INTENT in his EYES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN watches as he DISAPPEARS into the JUNGLE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN, CONFUSED for a minute ... THEN RUNS AFTER HIM.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN
{DIALOGUE}: Wait!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN is roughly SWUNG into the air, as KONG bounds off into the DEEP JUNGLE INTERIOR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN as she is suddenly SNATCHED UP by KONG and SWUNG ROUGHLY on to his SHOULDER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN HANGS ON for dear life as KONG GALLOPS into the JUNGLE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG moves SWIFTLY and POWERFULLY through the JUNGLE with ANN on his SHOULDER ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 90.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN as she looks up at the GIANT GORILLA ... the tension seems to go out of her body, she relaxes into his HAND ... for the first time since coming to SKULL ISLAND she feels SAFE.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BOTTOM OF CHASM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JACK STIRRING, immediately hearing the SCUTTLE OF INSECTS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE ROLLS OVER and see's HUGE SPIDERS CRAWLING INTO THE PIT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE staggers to his FEET ... REACHING INTO HIS PACK and PULLS from it A FLARE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THROWING it at the SPIDERS they CRAWL OFF.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DENHAM is lying nearby.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: Carl!!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DENHAM STIRS, MUMBLING IN PAIN BUT ALIVE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK SEES JIMMY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JIMMY is looking VACANTLY into space, JACK kneels down.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Jimmy?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JIMMY looks up at JACK, there are tears filling his eyes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He falls into JACK'S arms softly sobbing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM sitting up... dawning realization in his eyes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LUMPY, his back to CHOY ... he HOLDS CHOY'S HAND ... but CHOY'S FINGERS SLIDE LIMPLY out of LUMPY'S HAND ... LUMPY TURNS TO CHOY .
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ONLY TO SEE THAT HE has DIED.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: HAYES' eyes closed, his FACE peaceful, lying DEAD on the floor of the RAVINE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM PEERING over a ROCK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The wreckage of the CAMERA lies smashed and broken on the CHASM floor ... a thin, shiny, thread of black FILM trailing from the smashed CAMERA body like spilt innards.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DENHAM reaches out and touches the EXPOSED FILM ... his dreams DESTROYED.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: THE FLARE SLOWLY DIES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JACK cradling JIMMY in his ARMS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HE LOOKS UP as he SEES the INSECTS CRAWL BACK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: a HUGE six-foot CARNIVOROUS MAGGOT-THING squirms out!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It crawls blindly towards LUMPY and CHOY!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: LUMPY pulling CHOY'S BODY to safety, but both are ATTACKED by LARGE INSECTS, the size of dogs!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK tries to PULL THE GIANT CRAB-SPIDER OFF LUMPY, but instead it TURNS on him!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: More GIANT CRAB-SPIDERS JUMP at JACK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 91.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LUMPY and CHOY are CONSUMED by the nightmarish BUGS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM is WIELDING a short stick like a CLUB ... he smashes the HUGE BUGS in a psychotic explosion of RAGE, pulverizing their bodies into the DIRT!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All around, MONSTROSITIES OF NATURE emerge from DANK BURROWS and crawl towards the JACK, DENHAM and JIMMY ... these are HUGE INSECTILE MUTANTS - combinations of SPIDERS, CRABS, MANTISES and CENTIPEDES!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY JIMMY notices the TOMMY GUN sticking out of JACK'S PACK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GRABBING IT he aims at the INSECTS on JACK.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BAM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BAM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BAM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The GIANT INSECTS are blown apart!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK looks wildly around for DENHAM.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THEY SEE that they're SURROUNDED BY SPIDERS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK desperately swings at the INSECTS with a STICK, whacking and stabbing them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BAM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BAM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BAM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GUNSHOTS RING OUT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SPIDERS SWARM out of HOLES in the CLIFF AND DIE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK spins around ... confused.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ENGLEHORN and a COUPLE of SAILORS OPEN FIRE from the LIP of the CHASM, SHOOTING the SPIDERS into SMITHEREENS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: BRUCE SWINGS down from above, clinging to a VINE ... GUN BLAZING!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BRUCE proceeds to lay waste to the INSECTS ... those not blasted apart, scurrying away, back in to the darkness.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JUNGLE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Moving purposefully along a well-known route to his LAIR, KONG launches himself across a LOW CHASM ... one hand reaching out to clutch at THICK VINES on the other side ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The THICK VINES TEAR AWAY from the side of the CHASM WALL ... KONG falls backwards.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN still clutched protectively to his CHEST he lands with a THUD!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN looks up alarmed!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG scrambles to his feet, GROWLING ... he places ANN on the GROUND pushing her protectively behind him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG POV: LOOMING out of the CHASM WALL is a HUGE FACE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN as her expression suddenly changes from FEAR to DAWNING COMPREHENSION.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN walks past KONG ... who emits another LOW, WARNING GROWL.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN
{DIALOGUE}: It's alright ... it's okay ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN reaches the WALL and begins to pull away more of the VINES and CREEPERS to reveal ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 92.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A life-size and very life-like eroded STATUE of a SITTING GIANT GORILLA ... the IMAGE of KONG ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN turns back excitedly to KONG, trying to make him understand.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Look - it's you ... "Kong".
{DIALOGUE}: See ... you.
{DIALOGUE}: "Kong".
{DIALOGUE}: This is you.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG looks from ANN to the HUGE STATUE ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG POV: ANN is dwarfed by the STONE MONOLITH.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PUSH IN on KONG ... a growing sense of REALISATION as he comes to understand the STATUE is in fact a reflection of himself.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: KONG looking down at his hands ... it's as if he is seeing his GNARLED, LEATHERY FINGERS for the first time.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN moves towards KONG ... he looks at her ... there is a VULNERABLE EXPRESSION on his FACE ... FEAR and SADNESS well in his EYES.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. SKULL MOUNTAIN - DUSK
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In VERTIGO-INDUCING shots, KONG climbs HIGHER and HIGHER - up into the HIGHEST PEAK of SKULL ISLAND ... carefully cradling ANN in his hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A sudden FLAP OF WINGS and FLICKERING SHADOW causes KONG to pull ANN close to his chest as a sinister BAT-TYPE CREATURE lunges at her ... these SCAVENGERS hover in the SKIES around SKULL MOUNTAIN ... they have eight-foot wing spans and TALONED FEET.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Their faces are more reptile than bat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 93.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. KONG'S LAIR - DUSK
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: KONG steps out of a LARGE ROUND CAVE onto a LEDGE that juts out high over SKULL ISLAND ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: This is KONG'S LAIR ... Over the ledge is a DIZZYING DROP of at least 1000-feet down to the JUNGLE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The "VENTURE" can be seen - moored off the TIP of the ISLAND, some three miles away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: KONG gently places ANN on the GROUND ... ANN watches as he moves away and sits to one side of the LEDGE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SKY is a FIERY ORANGE as the SUN goes down ... SILHOUETTING the FIGURE of KONG ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN looks around the CAVE taking in her STRANGE SURROUNDINGS ... her eyes fall upon a HUGE GORILLA SKULL and SKELETON which lie within the recesses of the CAVE ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN turns and looks back at KONG ... realizing these are the BONES of his FOREBEARS ... that KONG was not always alone.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDEN flutter in the DARK recesses of the LAIR, a SINISTER SOUND, sends ANN scurrying towards KONG ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ONG won't look at her.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN breaks into a few tap steps ... NO RESPONSE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She leans down and picks up some STONES ... JUGGLING them, attempting to amuse him as she did before.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG's gaze remains averted ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He looks out over the JUNGLE CANOPY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN follows his GAZE, taking in the RUGGED LANDSCAPE which is bathed in the last EVENING RAYS of the SUN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She stares out to sea, a RAIN CLOUD casts shadows over the OCEAN.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN
{META_DATA}: (softly)
{DIALOGUE}: It's beautiful.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG sits QUIETLY staring out over the JUNGLE ... she looks up at him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Beautiful.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN places her HAND against her heart.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ANN (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: Beau-ti-ful.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG'S BIG PAW unfurls beside ANN ... she hesitates for a moment, then CLIMBS into it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: KONG gently lifts ANN ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 94.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: KONG with ANN, high above the JUNGLE, as the last of the DUSK LIGHT FADES.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. LOG CHASM - DAY
