{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. KONG'S LAIR - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK creeps CLOSE to the SLEEPING KONG'S BACK ... his SHOULDERS gently heaving with each breath.
