{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ... ANN is ASLEEP in KONG'S HAND!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOSE ON: KONG GROWLS ... JACK SPINS AROUND ... KONG is growling in his sleep!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK is less than 8 FEET away from ANN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: ANN'S eyes OPEN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: For a MOMENT she stares blankly at JACK ... then REALISATION arrives quickly - he has come for her!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She looks at JACK with disbelief.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOSE ON: JACK looks at ANN, drawing a finger to his lips ... neither DARES to move, or make a sound.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ERY SLOWLY, JACK rises and steps towards ANN.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He gestures for her to stay motionless in KONG'S PALM.
