{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JACK extends his HAND towards ANN ... she reaches out ... their FINGERS TOUCH ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ... and KONG'S EYES SNAP OPEN!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 97.
