{DIALOGUE}: Leave him alone!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 105.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: DENHAM steadies himself on his rock as KONG crawls past.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He hurls the CHLOROFORM BOTTLE ... it smashes against KONG'S FACE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG starts choking on the GAS.
