{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANOTHER DEAFENING ROAR!!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DENHAM looks up, AWESTRUCK, as he sees KONG TEARING FREE of the rest of his CHAINS!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The AUDIENCE BEGIN TO RISE from their SEATS ... PANIC sets in!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 115.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: AAAARRRRRGH!!!!!
