{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG reaches across and picks her up, HURLING the FAKE ANN and the ALTAR across the wide AUDITORIUM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LOW MOTION: LINKS snapping ... CHAINS breaking, BOLTS lifting from the FLOOR!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: With a MIGHTY FLOURISH, KONG rips off his WAIST RESTRAINTS and is at last completely FREE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The AUDIENCE RUSH the EXITS in a COLLECTIVE STAMPEDE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG swings from the STAGE into the FRONT ROW SEATS ... STOMPING and CRUSHING the slower moving PATRONS!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BROADWAY THEATRE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: PATRONS rush out of the THEATRE into the street.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. BROADWAY THEATRE STAGE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG ROARS and hurls a PLASTER CORNICE across the length of the THEATRE - straight at JACK!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ONG is now below the BALCONY LEVEL ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: n that moment KONG turns ... and sees JACK!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: For a brief second their EYES LOCK!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: KONG using his amazing STRENGTH to SWING up to the UPPER LEVEL BOXES ... with a LEAP he jumps on to the BALCONY ... the BALCONY crumbles under his WEIGHT ... sending DOZENS OF PEOPLE plummeting into the STALLS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ACK turns and RUNS for the DOOR as KONG struggles to REACH him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK reaches the EXIT, turns and looks back at KONG, a mixture of DREAD and AWE on his FACE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: DENHAM remains in the middle of the THEATRE mesmerized by the spectacle of KONG'S unleashing power!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BROADWAY - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK emerges from the THEATRE, all around him PANICKED PEOPLE run in TERROR!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BOOM!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK turns in time to see ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The VAST THEATRE WALL explodes onto the street, showering PEOPLE and CARS with BRICKS and STEEL ... KONG bursts into the MIDDLE OF THE ROAD!!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK stares up in horror as KONG heads straight for him ... JACK is going to DIE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 116.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: With an ANGUISHED ROAR the HUGE GORILLA stumbles past JACK into the BRIGHT LIGHTS of TIMES SQUARE ... he hasn't seen JACK!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG spins around reacting with terrified confusion to the STRANGENESS of CARS, TRUCKS, TRAMS, LIGHTS ... screaming people everywhere!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: J
{DIALOGUE}: ACK watches as KONG'S FEAR builds to a growing sense of ANGER and FRUSTRATION!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: KONG circles TIMES SQUARE ... snatching up any WOMAN with BLONDE HAIR ... desperately looking for ANN!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ODGING bits of FLYING DEBRIS, JACK tires to push his way through CROWDS of FLEEING PEOPLE towards KONG...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: AR WINDSCREEN POV ... KONG STOMPS on the CAR in FRONT, LIFTS FOOT and STOMPS over CAMERA.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: A TRAM heading straight for KONG ... the GIANT GORILLA THRUSTS out an ARM PROTECTIVELY ... KONG pulls his arm back ... TRAM firmly attached!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG'S FIST is CAUGHT in the TRAM'S WINDOWS!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JACK ... as he realises what KONG is doing ...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{META_DATA}: (under his breath)
{DIALOGUE}: Oh Jesus ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK as he watches KONG heading off down BROADWAY.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CRASHING off BUILDINGS KONG CAREENS out of TIMES SQUARE ...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. NEW YORK SHABBY THEATRE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: ANN emerges from a SHABBY THEATRE, just as SEVERAL POLICE CARS drive past at SPEED.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN runs to an INTERSECTION and looks up the STREET.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Several blocks away PANDEMONIUM is erupting outside a BROADWAY THEATRE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN starts to RUN.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BROADWAY/NEW YORK - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK spies a CAB that has STOPPED in the MIDDLE of the ROAD ... it's DRIVER watching the scene, MOUTH AGAPE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK jumping into the BACK of the CAB.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He gestures towards KONG!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: Follow that ape!
