{DIALOGUE}: It's all yours, Buddy!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 117.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: JACK scrambling into the FRONT SEAT of the CAB ... he throws it into GEAR and heads off after KONG!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: KONG reacts like a CORNERED ANIMAL in a BLIND PANIC ... FLAILING his arms in PANIC, the TRAM swinging through the air and SMASHING into BUILDINGS like a GIANT CLUB!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: NGLE ON: JACK drives the CAB DOWN BROADWAY ... swerving to MISS bits of TRAM that disintegrate off the FIST of KONG ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK accelerates, straight through the LEGS of the GIANT GORILLA!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: the CAB SPINS so that it now is facing KONG!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: KONG ... his FIST about to SMASH down on a TRAM full of PEOPLE!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The BLARE of a CAR HORN makes him turn ... he hesitates ... realizing who is behind the wheel of the CAB!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ACK'S POV ... as KONG comes closer.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: PANICKING DRIVERS PILE into each other.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK desperately tries his door, but it won't open, he is WEDGED IN by CARS on either side.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG LIFTS THE CAR directly in front - HIGH ABOVE HIS HEAD, throwing it into a BUILDING.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT/INT. STREETS/CAB - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: JACK'S FOOT depresses ACCELERATOR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The WHEELS are SPINNING WILDLY ... in a CLOUD OF BURNING RUBBER, the CAB speeds down the ROAD, weaving in and out of the path cut by KONG'S DESTRUCTION.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG BOUNDS AFTER THE CAB, running on all FOURS with incredible speed.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK crosses an INTERSECTION, driving up on the SIDEWALK to get a CLEARER DRIVING LANE ... PEDESTRIANS scatter - not only from the CAB, but from KONG who is in HOT PURSUIT.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: T
{DIALOGUE}: he CAB SLEWS across the STREET, disappearing up a TINY ALLEY, only just wide enough for the CAB, but TOO NARROW for KONG.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK glances back at KONG, ROARING with frustration at the ALLEY ENTRANCE.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT/INT. HERALD SQ/CAB - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK speeds out of the ALLEY and CROSSES the TRAFFIC FLOW, causing much BRAKING and HORN action.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He gets SLOWED in THICK TRAFFIC ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG BURSTS his way out of the ALLEY ENTRANCE ... RIGHT IN FRONT OF JACK'S CAB!!!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK SWERVES on to the SIDEWALK ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 118.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK steers the CAB wildly along the SIDEWALK scattering PEDESTRIANS in all directions!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG follows in HOT PURSUIT!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ACK sends the CAB into a couple of TIGHT TURNS ... he rounds a bend and DRIVES straight into a FRUIT VENDOR'S STALL!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE ON: The CAB, covered by the RUINED STALL, SLAMS into the WALL of a BUILDING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: JACK is thrown forward on IMPACT ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG rounds the corner and BOUNDS PAST JACK'S CAB ... hidden beneath the RUBBLE ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG searches for the CAB, ROARING in FRUSTRATION!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG'S HUGE EYES glance in the WINDOW, just as:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: KONG suddenly FREEZES!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He inclines his HEAD; unsure if what he is seeing is REAL.
