{CHARACTER_NAME}: K
{DIALOGUE}: ONG gently picks ANN up ... his EYES never leaving her FACE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANN holds tightly on to his HAND and they DISAPPEAR into the night.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. CENTRAL PARK - NIGHT
